{{For|the character in {{XC3FR|sublink}}|W (FR)}} {{spoiler}} {{Infobox Character |name = W |image = Consul_W.jpg |species = [[Moebius]] |age = |gender = Female |haircolor = |eyecolor = Red |affiliation = [[Consul]]s |appearances = {{XC3}} |voiceactorjp = |voiceactoreng = }} {{quote|Can play... with doll?|W}} '''W''' is a character in {{XC3}}.
== Overview == W is a [[Consul]]. She is fought during ''[[A Deep-Seated Scar]]''. She has the ability to control corpses and unconscious people, though the latter ability can be limited by her victims' psyche. This consul is very quiet and almost childlike, and enjoys playing with her "puppets". {{clr}}
== Story == [[R]] enlisted the aid of W to help her in her war against [[Colony 11]]. She made her first public appearance attacking [[Ashera]] from behind once R challenged the latter and [[Ouroboros]] to a duel. Then, W was able to control her to have ''her'' duel Ouroboros. R advised her not to kill her until she was satisfied, W was glad to "play" some more. [[Eunie]] was able to break W's control by shooting at and talking to her, allowing barriers to put around Ashera's psyche. R demanded that W keeps using her powers but she insisted that that it was impossible at that time. So, the two turned into their [[Moebius]] forms to take them out, but both were defeated anyway. W faded away before R, whom Ashera spoke to before fading as well. {{clr}}
